caption: b'2020 has been the year of #workfromhome. Will 2021 will be the year of #hybridwork?'

b'#COVID19 has forced many businesses to reevaluate how to run their operations, specifically those that heavily rely on #customerservice. In this #RCRealTalk, we sit down with @shephyken to discuss the future of #CX.\n\nWatch the full video here: ringcentr.al/RealTalkEp7FB (or click the link in our bio)'

b'Enjoying your time off will not only reset you mentally, it will make you feel more productive when you return to work. #weekend #relax #reflect #recharge #worklifebalance'

We thought it was a fun way to celebrate #PrideMonth and show our support for LGBTQ equality. :grinning_face: #RCause #RCproud'

b"It's important to give your brain time to rest, so try sticking to regular business hours when working from home. If you find it hard to step away from your computer at the end of the day, set an alarm or create a meeting reminder. #protip #workfromhomelife #worklifebalance"
